{"tid":2237254,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聶德權：公務員違反誓言很嚴重，象徵或有推翻政府意圖","createTime":"2020-10-10T06:08:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T06:16:02.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4adbe27846fb503642edcf81fc6cb97e81595561","tid":2237254,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T06:08:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553942-20201010.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553942-20201010.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDCbpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=a65ce687\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553942-20201010.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f69b28db\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553942-20201010.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局局長聶德權在一個電台節目表示，當局將於下星期一向各部門發通告，要求今年7月1日起新入職的公務員簽署聲明，確認擁護《基本法》和效忠特區。他說下一步會要求試用期當中的公務員簽署，而其他公務員，當局在諮詢公務員團體後會考慮不分職級一併處理，稍後會敲定有關安排。<br />\n<br />\n聶德權說，措施可令公務員更有自覺要效忠特區的意識，認為是一種承諾及彰顯承擔。他說公務員同樣是一個市民，對政策有不同意見可以有渠道表達，但也要尊重現行制度，不能因政治信念和個人想法，公開地持相反意見，影響公務員身分要求的工作，否則會令人有潛在或觀感上的衝突，公務員須兼顧好兩個身分，某程度是兩者不能共存。<br />\n<br />\n聶德權又說，公務員違反誓言是很嚴重的事，象徵有關人士可能有不支持一國兩制和推翻現屆政府的意圖。他指，假如言行違反公務員守則，須按紀律懲處機制處理，最嚴重可被革職。"},{"pid":"004a37702c384e15660b7aebebb530e8c95c9163","tid":2237254,"uid":53702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T06:09:20.000Z","msg":"即係你唔愛我，你就已經係意圖謀殺我"},{"pid":"1cdb4adecaf5ab4c40bf03a2b4976891e19eb1f9","tid":2237254,"uid":120627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T06:09:34.000Z","msg":"遲下唔投建制都係有推翻政府意圖"},{"pid":"f234292a529361154f171c3ebefadc8ffffc9b53","tid":2237254,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T06:09:47.000Z","msg":"「本人（姓名），謹以至誠作出宣言（或，謹向全能之主發誓），本人會竭誠依法為香港特別行政區政府效力為警務人員，遵從、支持及維護香港特別行政區的法律，以不畏懼、不徇私、不對他人懷惡意、不敵視他人及忠誠、努力的態度行使職權，執行職務，並且毫不懷疑地服從上級長官的一切合法命令。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927299c725b49a353fd2c5ea13470caa0c6ae5ab","tid":2237254,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T06:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6f5af4248b4e897d58157c6a8cfaa07a40e2a5","tid":2237254,"uid":108462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T06:10:11.000Z","msg":"好撚乞衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8f8758250a927102c32d81fe990eeea5f68871","tid":2237254,"uid":282064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T06:16:02.000Z","msg":"唔願意宣誓同埋違反誓言都係犯國安法"}]}